Description: The show starts with a scrap dealer coming on the road passing in the front of Kapil's house. An argument ensues between Kapil and the scrap dealer and the scrap dealer leaves parking his cart on the road. The scrap dealer asks Kapil take care of his cart and leaves for a movie with his girl friend. Later, Kapil talks about the antiques and there popularity. Kapil then asks the audience to share their experiences. An assistant of a Queen comes on the stage and is impressed after seeing the scrap, and leaves to call the Queen. Hearing this, Kapil immediately becomes an antique dealer and what follows is a laugh riot. Later, Rani Mukherjee joins the show to promote her upcoming movie, Mardaani. Watch the episode and know what happens next.
